@node "req" "System Requirements"

All you need to run Windoze is OS2+ and preferably large resolution. Depending on what Font you have in your settings, it might work or it moght not. One thing I do know, if you have 640 width and have topaz 8, then it won't work :( Try getting another font.

@endnode

@node "install" "Installing

Simply copy the drawer to wherever you like.

@endnode

@node "use" "Usage"

This program isn't really anything. It's just a program that makes fun out of Windows '95. All you do is run the program, and it will open a window in the center of your Workbench. It's set up with the $100 flag which means it'll stay as a Backdrop window. Messages will come up every 6 seconds or so, and to quit it, simply activate the window, and go to the pop-up menus, and select Quit.

@endnode

